# Drop heavy + irrelevant paths from the build context the core Dockerfile sees.
.git
node_modules
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.turbo
**/.next
**/coverage
neat-out
# demo/ stays in context so the core Dockerfile can copy demo/*/package.json
# for the workspace install. Demo source is not needed inside the core image —
# at runtime it's mounted via docker-compose volumes.
.github
docs
README.md
*.log
